snippet.title: Slackers Carts of Glory  -   Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
🔥 No brakes. No steering. No fear.
🛒💨 Take a deep breath and dive into the wildest ride ever!

⭐ Add it to your Steam Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2354000/Slackers__Carts_of_Glory/

🚀Get ready for Slackers Carts of Glory! 🚀
⚡ Coming to Steam on September 18 ⚡

⚠️THINGS TO REMEMBER ONCE YOU'RE IN THE CART⚠️

✨ First of all: 🚫🚗 It's NOT a car.
✨ The cart has no brakes. (deal with it) 🛒💨
✨ The cart has no engine. (push and sweat to move) 💪💦
✨ The cart has no seatbelts. (we all know how it's going to end) 😬😱
✨ The cart has no steering wheel (good luck taming the beast) 🌀🛒😈
✨ Last but not least: IT'S NOT A CAR. 🚫🚗
Ready for the wild ride? 🎮🔥
